  "spec_text": "# qNS multi-feature decision surface.\n#\n# Carrier:\n# - qns8 is the finite powerset Boolean algebra over eight audited atoms.\n#\n# This spec combines:\n# - neural-proposer masks,\n# - exact symbolic filtering,\n# - review and rejection routing,\n# - pointwise revision over a finite policy-memory mask.\n#\n# Scope:\n# - finite audited atom universe only,\n# - toy proposer lives outside Tau,\n# - Tau computes exact qns8 Boolean expressions,\n# - this is not upstream nlang and not unrestricted natural-language semantics.\n\nset charvar off\n\nall8() := { #xFF }:qns8.\nnot8(x) := x ^ all8().\n\nproposed(u,p) := u & p.\neligible(u,p,a,h) := proposed(u,p) & a & not8(h).\nauto_accept(u,p,a,r,h) := eligible(u,p,a,h) & not8(r).\nhuman_review(u,p,a,r,h) := eligible(u,p,a,h) & r.\nsymbolic_reject(u,p,a,h) := proposed(u,p) & (not8(a) | h).\npartition(u,p,a,r,h) :=\n  auto_accept(u,p,a,r,h) |\n  human_review(u,p,a,r,h) |\n  symbolic_reject(u,p,a,h).\nunsafe_leak(u,p,a,r,h) := auto_accept(u,p,a,r,h) & h.\n\nrevise(old,guard,replacement) :=\n  (guard & replacement) | (not8(guard) & old).\n\npriority_revision(old,u,p,a,r,h,auto_add,review_add,reject_add) :=\n  revise(\n    revise(\n      revise(old, symbolic_reject(u,p,a,h), reject_add),\n      human_review(u,p,a,r,h),\n      review_add),\n    auto_accept(u,p,a,r,h),\n    auto_add).\n\nidempotence_probe(old,u,p,a,r,h,auto_add,review_add,reject_add) :=\n  priority_revision(\n    priority_revision(old,u,p,a,r,h,auto_add,review_add,reject_add),\n    u,p,a,r,h,auto_add,review_add,reject_add).\n"
}
